lead_paragraph: Iziane Castro Marques scored a career-high 26 points and Lauren Jackson added 18 points and 9 rebounds to lead the Seattle Storm to a 91-54 victory over the Liberty last night at Madison Square Garden. It was the Liberty’s franchise-worst 10th straight loss.
